===Verb===
'''boxing'''

# Present participle of ''to [[box]]''.

===Noun===
'''boxing''' (''uncountable'')

# A sport where two opponents punch each other with [[gloved]] [[fist]]s, the object being to knock one's opponent [[unconscious]].

